name: Trees - signed limited edition
description:
Trees in the fog of the Wicklow Mountains, Ireland.

Colour signed limited edition of 30 prints on Fujicolor Professional Crystal Archive DP II 220g/m² paper.

Signed and numbered at the back of the photo.

The image size corresponds to the measures shown above, a slim white border has to be added to these measures. So, the image looks more refined and can be mounted easily in passe-partout frames.
